# Cursor rules for this repo
#
# Canonical guidance lives in `AGENTS.md` (and `CLAUDE.md`).
#
# Key reminders:
# - Use Node.js 22+ and prefer repository scripts (`pnpm run ...`, `./setup.sh`, `make ...`).
# - Do not use `any` and do not suppress lint/TypeScript errors.
# - Commit messages must match: `[DR-XX] type: subject` (see `commitlint.config.js`).
#
# Quick commands:
# - Setup: `./setup.sh` (or `./setup.sh --quick`)
# - Dev: `pnpm run dev` (or `pnpm run devfe`, `pnpm run devbe`)
# - Lint/format/test: `pnpm run lint`, `pnpm run format`, `pnpm run test`

